flowchart TD
    A[🛒 Customer enters card details] --> B[Client-side tokenization\nHosted fields / iframe]
    B --> C[Token sent to merchant server\n🔒 PAN never touches merchant]
    C --> D[Merchant server sends\ntoken + amount to Payment Gateway]

    D --> E[Payment Gateway validates\nrequest & routes]
    E --> F[Gateway forwards to\nPayment Processor]
    F --> G{Card Network routing}
    G -->|Visa| H[Visa Network]
    G -->|Mastercard| I[Mastercard Network]
    G -->|Amex| J[Amex Network]
    H --> K[Route to Issuing Bank]
    I --> K
    J --> K

    K --> L{Issuing Bank checks}
    L --> M[Check available balance]
    L --> N[Fraud detection rules]
    L --> O[Velocity & spending limits]
    L --> P[Card status - active/blocked]

    M & N & O & P --> Q{Issuer decision}
    Q -->|Approved| R[✅ Authorization code generated]
    Q -->|Declined - Insufficient funds| S[❌ Soft decline]
    Q -->|Declined - Fraud suspected| T[❌ Hard decline]
    Q -->|Declined - Card expired| U[❌ Hard decline]

    R --> V[Auth code sent back\nthrough card network]
    V --> W[Processor receives approval]
    W --> X[Gateway returns auth\nto merchant]
    X --> Y[Authorization hold placed\non customer card]

    Y --> Z{Capture timing}
    Z -->|Immediate capture| AA[Transaction added to\nsettlement batch]
    Z -->|Delayed capture| AB[Merchant captures\nwithin 7 days]
    AB --> AA

    AA --> AC[End of day: Batch submitted\nto Acquiring Bank]
    AC --> AD[Acquirer submits to\ncard network for settlement]
    AD --> AE[Card network settles\nwith Issuing Bank]
    AE --> AF[Interchange fee deducted]
    AF --> AG[Net amount sent\nto Acquiring Bank]
    AG --> AH[Acquirer deposits to merchant\nminus processing fees]
    AH --> AI[💰 Merchant receives payout\nT+1 to T+3 business days]

    S --> AJ[Return decline code\nto merchant]
    T --> AJ
    U --> AJ
    AJ --> AK[Merchant displays error\nto customer]
    AK --> AL{Customer action}
    AL -->|Try another card| A
    AL -->|Abandon| AM[❌ Payment abandoned]

    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style R fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style AI fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style S fill:#F5A623,color:#fff
    style T fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style U fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style AM fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style Y fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
